## 0.1.7
  - Fix is_runit_installed check /usr/bin/sv instead of /sbin/runit #6
  - Upgrade cfssl 1.2.0
  - Add ssl-helper that allow certificate auto-renew and let choose
    certificate generator (cfssl-helper default, or jsonssl-helper)
